  "instructions": [
    "Heat the oil in the ceramic tagine over medium heat.",
    "Add the onion and garlic and sauté until softened, about 5 minutes.",
    "Add the cumin seeds and coriander seeds and sauté for 1 minute.",
    "Add the duck legs and cook until browned on all sides, about 5 minutes.",
    "Add the chili peppers, pineapple juice, canned tomatoes, shio cure, and lemon juice.",
    "Stir to combine and bring to a simmer.",
    "Cover the tagine and cook over low heat for 2 hours, or until the duck is tender.",
    "Season with black pepper to taste.",
